Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:22.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}魔法の言葉 覚えている 虹の始まったところ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:30.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}あの時世界の全てに 一瞬で色が付い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:37.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}本当の声はいつだって 正しい道を照らしている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:45.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}なんだって疑っているから とても強く信じている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:52.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}心臓が動いている事の 吸って吐いてが続く事の
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:59.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}心がずっと熱い事の 確かな理由を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:06.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}雲の向こうの銀河のように どっかで無くした切符のように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:14.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}生まれる前の歴史のように 君が持っているから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:20.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}それだけ わかっている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:28.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}僕だけ わかっている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:22.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}记得魔法的话语 彩虹开始的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:30.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}那时世界的一切 瞬间带上了色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:37.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}真正的声音无论何时 都在指引正确的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:45.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}无论何事都要怀疑 所以才坚定的相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:52.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}心脏在搏动 呼吸在持续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:59.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}内心总是如此炽热的 确切的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:06.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}如同云之彼端的银河 如同丢失在某处的车票
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:14.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}如同降生前的历史 由你持有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:20.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}只有此事 很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:28.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}只有我 很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:10.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}その声は流れ星のように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:15.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}次々に耳に 飛び込んでは光って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:19.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}魚のように集まりだして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:24.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}冷たかった胸に 陽だまりが出来た
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:29.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}普通の触れ方を知らないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:33.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}戸惑っていたら 触れてくれた手に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:38.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}どれだけ夜をくぐり抜けても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:44.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}ずっと冷めないままの熱が 脈を打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:48.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}君がいるそれだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:54.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}命の全部が輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:57.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}凍りついた心に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:24:03.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}その鼓動が響き火を灯す
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:08.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}いくつもなくなったあとに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:13.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}強く残った ひとつ残った
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.96,0:24:18.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}離れない いつでも側に
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:26.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}僕の中に 一番近くに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:10.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}那个声音像流星一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:15.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}接二连三的跃入耳里 熠熠生辉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:19.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}像鱼一样开始聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:24.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}冰冷的胸间有了阳光的暖意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:29.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}因为不知道普通的接触方式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:33.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}所以迷惘 对于碰触我的那只手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:38.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}无论穿越多少黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:44.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}一直不曾冷却的热量 在鼓动着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:48.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}只因为有你存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:54.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}生命的一切都绽放光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:57.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}在冰冻的心间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:24:03.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}那份鼓动回响着 点燃火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:08.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}失去太多太多之后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:13.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}顽强的留下 唯一留下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.96,0:24:18.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}不会分离 无论何时都在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:26.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}在我心里 最为接近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(192,294)\fad(1500,0)}过去的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我完成了年内所有比赛之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得了重感冒 一直在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独自蜷缩在昏暗的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎来了12月31号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口好渴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃点什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有药…得快点吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只剩最后一片药了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须去买 但是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 还是再睡一觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再睡一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下次醒来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现感冒已经如谎言般退去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家闭门不出的这段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因发热变得意识模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了许多次同一个梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我小时候反复见过的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个乘坐很长很长的电动扶梯的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非对什么感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是上升 上升
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上升的顶端
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有回去的路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别按了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 起不来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 果然感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 突入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 是小零的家诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 确保枕头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 拿好手机钱包钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样穿着睡衣也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:04:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加件外套
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 把围巾围好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经为你叫好的士了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的士？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然问去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是去看医生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是流感的话就要隔离照看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是普通的感冒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就带你来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 不是流感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为家里有老人幼儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须得特别注意才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吃蛋花粥吧 快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看过你的厨房了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都没有吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腌梅干可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加点进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒觉得胃口不好的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加点梅干会清爽些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 稍微把脖子伸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用毛巾围住脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流汗的话再换一条
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为吃蛋花粥容易流汗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须多流些汗来退烧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛巾还有很多 随时可以换哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你擦擦额头的汗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃子 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃子也想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 那个是零的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 吃了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么喝点茶就躺下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给老家打个电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一定很担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我已经独立了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜柑 没有什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜柑 蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独立呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借下你的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手机差不多关机3天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让周围的人这么担心你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能称作是独立哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 我是零
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零吗 是零吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电话一直打不通 我打算过来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过电话听到父亲声音的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才知道了自己的肤浅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:08:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲的声音 是真在担心的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不停地胡思乱想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 结果还是只考虑着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐山 身体咋样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吃个饭 再吃一次药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻衣子出场的话叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石川小百合出场了再叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了吃晚饭的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请叫我起床喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道会成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前还更夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为比现在还多三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挤在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 感觉都要缺氧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:08:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们的父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年都看着他们的睡脸抱怨着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 外婆和我三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,边收拾着边看「过去一年将来一年」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有什么缘由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个家里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都对父亲的事绝口不提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 零也吃一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你睡的很香 就没有叫你起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得把梅干弄碎加进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便因为发烧吃不出味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道也会觉得清爽些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些我刚刚说过了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是我每次感冒的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈就会说给我听的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 果然会说一样的话呐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要听见这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边觉得「又在说同样的话了」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却又感到了安心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像魔法一样呢 妈妈的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃她没有什么机会听妈妈的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在除夕这么重要的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不是家人 却还来打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还让你们费神照顾我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我希望你来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到帮助的人是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是孤独一人 收拾着这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会哭出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么哭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 连我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边吸着鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人一边慌张地寻找纸巾时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视里传来了除夕的钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样难堪地 今年在夜空中远去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满心只想着自己孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从没能注意到其他人也是孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此愚蠢的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除夕的钟声 深沉厚重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿若一条缓慢的深河
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(176,294)}将来一年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(1108,702)}过往一年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的一年终将到来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们呐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁在妈妈的衣柜上乱贴贴纸的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 这个很难撕下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千寻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 能起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐说要吃早饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还发烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退了一大半了 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报纸上好多广告啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 小桃 这样我都没法看报纸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐山要吃年糕吗 要什么味道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要砂糖酱油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃要起司的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也要起司的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们继续吧 有请下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还是有一点烧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 总而言之先吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再吃药
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快进被炉里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只穿睡衣的话脚会很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是邮递员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啦 贺年卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的 姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐的 爷爷的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有给小桃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥啊啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥啊 呐 啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样啊 收到很多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多呐 不知道贺年状抽奖会不会中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃也有收到了呐 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:43.34,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}幼儿园和儿科大夫寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 零家说不定也有收到了呀 贺年状
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 我觉得应该没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去帮你拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.27,Top,,0,0,0,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.19,Top,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.69,Top,,0,0,0,,只会让某些事情完全暴露出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等哦 我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钥匙借我哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:15.17,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an9}不忍直视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有…有收到啊 贺年卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两…两张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有收到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为不会有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一张是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是龙猫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这别墅是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城堡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热气球？CG合成的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:26.22,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}桐山！！期待与你C1战值日的到来！！二海棠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那另外一张是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.10,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}由衷祝贺新春\N雨伞旗鱼 180CM\NPE线3号 200cm\N前导线 80磅\N于马来西亚海上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本将棋联盟会长 第十六代国手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神宫寺崇德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将棋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.73,Top,,0,0,0,,雨伞旗鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊？这位…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.36,Top,,0,0,0,,马来西亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真敢秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:43.86,Top,,0,0,0,,钓鱼的老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先说清楚 这个人很强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然从以前开始就有点怪怪的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是这幅德行但却当了七代国手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为啥要帮他辩护啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快乐 美咲阿姨来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是老家好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆家那边会让人觉得肩膀发酸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:13.14,Top,,0,0,0,,美咲阿姨你看桃子的贺年卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.52,Top,,0,0,0,,阿姨 请用茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让你总是装乖巧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.98,Top,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 日向真是贴心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从以前开始 就只有在外面的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有红包哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 日向 桃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…来 顺便给你一份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将棋少年 虽然只有一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你从除夕那天开始就感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被明里绑架过来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我也有？这怎么能收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦 虽然有一阵子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是跟一砂先生和史密斯先生一起来光顾过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后也拜托了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 妈妈 美香子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲来拜访你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年还打算让明里去你那工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再让亲人帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雇个新人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可从来没有赞成过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让明里再做什么危险的工作呐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 我的店一点也不危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然店面很小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我高贵城堡里都是优雅的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此 可…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让明里因为家务和照顾孩子闭门不出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后渐渐变老吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子个性认真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的会扮演起母亲的角色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一周两次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪帕强迫也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也必须化化妆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上漂亮衣服出去走走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是难得的美人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本人却日渐憔悴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错过了嫁人的时机怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我店里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人能碰明里一根手指头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 准确说是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不让他们碰到的前提下狠赚一笔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把男人那种
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为无法触碰而变得躁动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始花钱大手大脚的习性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牢牢抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老太婆 你的女儿是恶鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你生了个恶鬼的女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨 吃晚饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要试试我跟小日向的力作？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我老公去看足球比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真是用心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然做了年节菜呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是现在比较流行的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我跟小日向一起想的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面都是经过深思熟虑后选的吉祥菜色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是做出来很美味可口的年节菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是买整条的红白鱼糕的话肯定吃不完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们就改买红宫鱼肉山芋丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用竹签串起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出来像是团子串一样的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求能过上踏实的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以做了豌豆猪肉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求来年财运
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以做了金色的栗金团
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求未来有更好展望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以做了莲藕炒牛蒡丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求根基扎实代代相传
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就做了包牛蒡肉卷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望外公能长寿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以做了乌龟状的迷你汉堡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然还有伊达卷和双色甜蛋卷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我还试着把法兰克福香肠做成鲷鱼状
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:04.96,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}只负责吃的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两真是太了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前美香子跟外婆也是两人努力做出整桌年节菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加些意达利面进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要口香糖 口香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年节菜原来是这样呐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还带着愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只要看见这个餐盒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会产生必须要装满它的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装满餐盒后的成就感真是让人欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算完成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 这种感觉真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成就感可是每天生活中非常重要的动力来源
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我能理解 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是成就感跟麻烦总是一同岀现的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也正是跨过了困难
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能获得成就感呐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见呢 多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会再来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也请多多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 已经这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 能替我带小桃去洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盘子姐姐来洗就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要用到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以麻烦你先去二楼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 想必你也是第一次看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实川本家的浴室就在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.59,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an9}在打开客厅的落地窗之后\N突然就出现了浴室！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.59,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an9}而且还没有更衣室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前家里没有浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直都是去澡堂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过后来家人多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就在院子里增加了这个浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里都是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也很希望能够有一间更衣室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是如果这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会没有院子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还要花很多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是每次有客人来就会觉得很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起呢 小零
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零不许看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚…晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓…吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是惊人的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 药也吃过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这根绳子还真是方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我可以在才认识不久的人家里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样平常地睡觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆在这里 为什么会这样安心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会有那样怀念的梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.53,0:22:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样呐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么回事呐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座古老的房屋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把时间 大家和一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至连我在内
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静静地包围起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催人熟睡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 我落入沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.99,0:22:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是已经忘了久别多少时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深沉 柔和的沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:22:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(1108,706)}将来一年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.35,0:24:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 去得到它吧 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.81,0:24:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常清楚这种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.64,0:24:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下还能剩下几天的伙食费
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.40,0:24:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.19,0:24:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我有一场无论如何都不想输的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.19,0:24:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.24,0:24:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好忙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.70,0:24:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙得不可开交
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.62,0:24:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我来代替
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.83,0:24:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三月的狮子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.16,0:24:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集也要继续观看喵
